@ENDNODE

@NODE "DownloadPrefs-SAVE" "How to use DownloadPrefs?"

 @{u}SAVE@{uu}

 Saves the HRDownload.liste.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "DownloadPrefs-QUIT" "How to use DownloadPrefs?"

 @{u}QUIT@{uu}

 Quits DownloadPrefs.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "DownloadPrefs-Menue" "How to use DownloadPrefs?"
@TOC "MAIN"

 @{u}The menu of DownloadPrefs:@{uu}

        +@{b}-----------------@{ub}...
        | Project    |
        |@{b}-----------------@{ub}...
        | About      |
        +@{b}------------@{ub}+
        | Open       |
        | Last Saved |
