@NODE "know problems" "Known problems"
@TOC "MAIN"

 @{u}Known problems@{uu}

 @{b}- I want to read a HTMLmail and HTMLread starts MultiView or
   HTMLView-Demo but nothing is displayed in the viewerwindow.@{ub}

   The reason:
   This is not a fault of HTMLread! The HTMLdatatype and
   HTMLview not able to interpret the HTMLcode correctly and break up.
   MultiView shows an empty window and HTMLview-Demo only shows his
   startupmessage.

   The solution:
   Use a brower for viewing HTML Documents.

@ENDNODE

